snippet.title: Super Time Force Ultra - More PlayStation Exclusive Characters! | PS4
snippet.description:
Super Time Force Ultra is coming soon to PS4 & VITA... and Capy has added a couple more PlayStation exclusive team members to the mix! 

Capy already revealed that Shuhei Yoshida himself will be a playable character... But Shu didn’t come alone. In fact, he brought a couple very close friends: everyones favorite berobed traveler from Journey, and Sir Galahad from The Order: 1886!

For more info, head to http://www.supertimeforce.com
